Mmm. Yeah, well, right now
there's an effort under way

00:38:35.432 --> 00:38:37.429
demanding universal
educational guidelines.

00:38:38.429 --> 00:38:39.428
Sounds reasonable.

00:38:39.436 --> 00:38:40.449
Oh, it's meant to.

00:38:41.423 --> 00:38:44.420
